headline: Is Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) Still Undervalued After Its Recent 27% Three-Month Share Price Climb?
summary: Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) has been quietly grinding higher, up about 27% over the past 3 months, as investors warm to its steady double digit revenue and earnings growth rather than chasing flashier stories. See our latest analysis for Intuitive Surgical. At around $556.86 a share, Intuitive’s 90 day share price return of roughly 27% sits on top of an already strong foundation, with a three year total shareholder return above 110% showing this momentum has been building, not simply appearing...
